%description
Calculates first, and second order, average minimal depth of a maximal
subtree for a forest object produced by the R 'ranger' package. This
variable importance metric is implemented as described in Ishwaran et. al.
("High-Dimensional Variable Selection for Survival Data", March 2010,
<doi:10.1198/jasa.2009.tm08622>).

